goal.en:
"On successful completion of this course, students will be able to
1. understand and use familiar, everyday expressions and very simple sentences, which relate to the satisfying of concrete needs of daily life such as asking for directions, making appointments, seeing a doctor, talking about clothes and weather;
2. understand daily conversations, if the person they are speaking to speaks slowly and clearly and is willing to help;
3. understand letters and grasp their gist and most important information;
4. compose letters, postcards, e-mails in correct form"
